			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Basically it went like this.
<br />
Drood is being annoyingin DSP on ooc, so I shut him down by using his own stupidity agianst him. He decided to duel me, so I'm thinking, fine, whatever, i'll just have the chanter in group bandage me.(He had maxed out bind wound) So I memmed the songs i would need, keep in mind im lvl 30. I memed Elemental Shield, lvl 10ish song, fire cold and magic resist, cause droods use fire, and magic is root. Dual starts, pop on selo's, chase him around, got off some hits to interrupt, then got rooted after he got a few off. Grab my lute and play regen, but his DoT's pretty much negate it and still do plenty of damage. I didnt get free for like 2 minutes which was weird, i dont think he recast root. Basically he only ran because the chanter was keeping me alive.
<br />

<br />
Any way to beat him? I tried to mez, but some people say you cant mez people anymore. He was red to me, group member of mine said he was red to him at 32, so maybe mez just got resisted? Basically, is there any way to combat this without the luck of resists and interrupts?</span></td>
